dc_title_s: New Jersey - Cape May County - Peck Beach - Emergency dune protection sections III
dc_description_s: Map of Ocean City covering area from 59th Street to 42nd Street. Map shows soundings, pilings, the edge of Berm, groins, and the condition of piers and bulkhead. Drainage ditches, Peck Beach, and marsh areas are located on the map. Attached are sheets 27 A and 27 B.
